# Readme file - Android app: Bolly-wood.
Main:-
This app is a game between user and AI, inspired from the classic AI problem "Hangman". 
Rules:-
The  user and AI, give each other movies to guess revealing only the vowels in the movie-name. You get 10 guesses to get the movie name. In each guess, the player guesses an alphabet. If that alphabet is present, the alphabet replaces the blanks in the movie name wherever it is present. Otherwise, the player looses a guess. 
